09:32.300 --> 09:33.779
Can I ask you something?

09:33.780 --> 09:34.620
Fire away.

09:34.621 --> 09:37.099
What's your favourite book?

09:37.100 --> 09:39.019
Batman.

09:39.020 --> 09:41.140
If there was an election tomorrow,
who would you vote for?

09:41.141 --> 09:43.580
