09:44.700 --> 09:46.739
World events, and stuff?

09:46.740 --> 09:49.019
Makes me sleepy. I don't care.

09:49.020 --> 09:53.139
Oh, there's a dubstep all-nighter on
in town. I said we might go.

09:53.140 --> 09:56.379
You could go on your own. We don't
have to do everything together.

09:56.380 --> 09:59.140
But you said that's the secret
to a happy relationship.

10:00.780 --> 10:02.419
Maybe I was wrong.

10:02.420 --> 10:04.380
Go out, have a great time.

10:26.380 --> 10:27.500
Sorry. Did I wake you?

10:27.501 --> 10:28.700
No.

10:29.940 --> 10:30.980
Couldn't sleep.

10:30.981 --> 10:32.699
