10:32.700 --> 10:35.259
Just me mind working overtime.

10:35.260 --> 10:36.819
Did you get off with anyone?

10:36.820 --> 10:38.539
What?!

10:38.540 --> 10:40.539
No, course not.
Did you?

10:40.540 --> 10:41.379
No!

10:41.380 --> 10:42.300
Kiss anyone?

10:42.301 --> 10:45.579
Fuck off. I wouldn't look at anyone!

10:45.580 --> 10:47.859
I think it's about time you did.

10:47.860 --> 10:49.260
What?!

11:00.264 --> 11:03.903
I'll keep it safe until your dad
comes back for it, yeah?

11:03.904 --> 11:05.224
No worries.

11:07.104 --> 11:09.464
