11:09.465 --> 11:10.784
Sorted.

11:13.264 --> 11:14.823
So this friend...

11:14.824 --> 11:15.903
Of a friend.

11:15.904 --> 11:17.263
Friend of a friend.

11:17.264 --> 11:19.823
She wants him to shag around,
tells him to go for it?

11:19.824 --> 11:20.623
Yeah.

11:20.624 --> 11:24.063
It's every man's dream, innit,
having a bird pushing him

11:24.064 --> 11:27.704
