tell him to fill his boots!

11:38.144 --> 11:41.343
Of course, it means she's
splitting up with him.

11:41.344 --> 11:43.703
No, she wants them to stay together.

11:43.704 --> 11:46.703
She's dumping him. If your mate
can't see that, he's a muppet.

11:46.704 --> 11:49.024
Either that or she's already
doing someone herself.

12:00.024 --> 12:01.744
And the woman said,
"Shall I get you a priest?"

12:01.745 --> 12:03.823
