wiping away his tears says,

12:03.824 --> 12:06.904
"No! Sex is the last thing
on my mind!"

12:11.264 --> 12:14.943
I hope that's a fucking money tree.
We could do wi' one!

12:14.944 --> 12:20.464
It's a cherry. I thought we could
plant it together in memory of...

12:21.584 --> 12:24.823
We'd have somewhere
we could go to think of her.

12:24.824 --> 12:26.104
Oh, for fuck's sake.

12:32.104 --> 12:33.463
There's your pal's lad.

12:33.464 --> 12:35.463
Oh, crap.

12:35.464 --> 12:40.543
Hello, ladies, I hope you don't
mind. I tried a few places.

12:40.544 --> 12:42.903
Nice work, Sherlock.

12:42.904 --> 12:46.143
It's just... I've
so many questions about my mother.

12:46.144 --> 12:48.583
My memory's not what it was.

12:48.584 --> 12:49.504
Any scraps from the table.

12:49.505 --> 12:52.943
From what I can gather,
she did do Paul McCartney,

12:52.944 --> 12:55.344
but Bobby Charlton is just a rumour.

12:58.464 --> 13:00.544
A bottle of pale ale as well.
That's really good.

13:00.545 --> 13:04.023
And it's good for you, full of iron.

13:04.024 --> 13:05.263
I'm not sure.

13:05.264 --> 13:06.262
I didn't like it at first...

13:06.263 --> 13:07.502
Fuck's going on?!

13:07.503 --> 13:08.502
All right, Billy?

13:08.503 --> 13:10.104
Is it him? Are you doing him?
Is that what this is about?

13:10.105 --> 13:11.543
What are you on about?

13:11.544 --> 13:13.063
