you know.

13:40.784 --> 13:42.104
I can't pretend it never happened.

13:42.105 --> 13:44.384
And I won't live every
day like it just has.

13:50.544 --> 13:52.704
Where the fuck are you going?!

13:57.624 --> 14:03.303
I was saving stuff,
putting a little bit aside,

14:03.304 --> 14:05.264
ever since the first scan.

14:10.024 --> 14:16.343
Nicked some copper wire from Maine
Road for this... and the snow suit.

14:16.344 --> 14:19.063
It's beautiful stuff.

14:19.064 --> 14:20.863
Quality gear. We could sell it?

14:20.864 --> 14:22.943
It's got to be
a hundred quid's worth.

14:22.944 --> 14:25.144
It's a night out
at the very least!

14:35.864 --> 14:39.103
I can't tell you what
a tonic this is.

14:39.104 --> 14:40.543
Yes.

14:40.544 --> 14:42.743
You see, I always hated her
for abandoning us,

14:42.744 --> 14:47.863
for what she did to my father...
but you paint a picture of a woman

14:47.864 --> 14:50.623
who was living life to the full.

14:50.624 --> 14:57.463
I really do now have to be going.
Thank you, goodbye.

14:57.464 --> 15:00.023
It makes me feel somehow
better about it...

15:00.024 --> 15:02.823
inheriting money from
a woman I barely knew,

15:02.824 --> 15:05.824
a houseful of possessions...

15:07.064 --> 15:11.303
Perhaps I could stay
for just one more.

15:11.304 --> 15:13.944
There's so much to tell.

15:19.464 --> 15:21.864
Does that make you feel better?

15:24.784 --> 15:26.584
What goes on in your head?

15:27.664 --> 15:30.743
Are you having an affair?
D'you want shot of me?

15:30.744 --> 15:33.703
