ground, baby. It worries me.

15:42.944 --> 15:44.183
Common ground?

15:44.184 --> 15:45.303
I mean like...

15:45.304 --> 15:46.943
I know what it means.

15:46.944 --> 15:51.423
I like Batman, I like all graphic
novels. They're... works of art.

15:51.424 --> 15:55.743
And I wouldn't vote in the election
cos politics is bollocks.

15:55.744 --> 15:58.423
It's all bought and paid
for in advance.

15:58.424 --> 16:01.303
You vote for whatever cunt
offends you least.

16:01.304 --> 16:04.024
