wearing this stuff...

16:44.864 --> 16:46.223
Sorry...

16:46.224 --> 16:49.143
I just blurted it out.

16:49.144 --> 16:51.303
I thought a night out
would do us good.

16:51.304 --> 16:53.664
I'll get a sub off Lillian,
that'll see us right.

17:06.104 --> 17:09.743
Compliments on a postcard,
please, ladies.

17:12.864 --> 17:17.143
You don't think it's a bit OTT for a
job interview, I mean, at your age?

17:17.144 --> 17:19.943
Making the most of her assets.
Your dad's not earning,

17:19.944 --> 17:23.143
so it's down to your mum
to bring in the bacon.

17:23.144 --> 17:25.782
I am stuffed into this.
Too much...?

17:25.784 --> 17:31.223
Not enough, in my humble.
Designed to hypnotise, cleavage...

17:31.224 --> 17:32.824
it's what God intended.

17:34.584 --> 17:35.943
Too low?

17:35.944 --> 17:37.863
If I was a fella...

17:37.864 --> 17:40.703
I'd ride you. Don't know
if I'd give you a job,

17:40.704 --> 17:42.904
but I would definitely ride you.

17:47.024 --> 17:49.143
What are you so nervous about?

17:49.144 --> 17:52.783
I hate job interviews.
I get all sweaty, I crumble.

17:52.784 --> 17:54.023
You're smart.

17:54.024 --> 17:56.943
Not when people are judging me,
looking at me.

17:56.944 --> 17:58.264
Hate it, always have done.

17:59.704 --> 18:01.583
Right. What's the damage?

18:01.584 --> 18:04.503
Oh, it'll save
until you get your first pay packet.

18:04.504 --> 18:05.942
You'll do it just like this
tomorrow?

18:05.943 --> 18:08.144
I'll have you skipping
down the street to that interview,

18:08.145 --> 18:10.143
looking a million dollars.

18:10.144 --> 18:12.784
Right! Best get out of this,
hang it up.

18:14.784 --> 18:16.184
Get off!

18:42.424 --> 18:47.303
Some guys don't like how
their missus looks in the morning,

18:47.304 --> 18:50.863
but I love it ... little puffy eyes,
adjusting, like a little chipmunk.

18:50.864 --> 18:56.223
I can suck a banana right
out of its skin, no hands.

18:56.224 --> 18:58.303
Hello, Daddy.

18:58.304 --> 19:02.223
She was dry-humping him
like a horny schoolie!

19:02.224 --> 19:03.304
She is a horny schoolie!

19:03.305 --> 19:04.703
Is there any other kind?

19:04.704 --> 19:07.223
I don't see what's so funny here.

19:07.224 --> 19:10.223
Your brand-new
out-of-the-box husband

19:10.224 --> 19:12.583
was firing into another woman.

19:12.584 --> 19:13.943
I told him to.

19:13.944 --> 19:17.703
I was gonna take a fucking
drill to his head,

19:17.704 --> 19:19.383
but I thought, "No, you know what?

19:19.384 --> 19:21.623
"You might want..."
What did you just say?

19:21.624 --> 19:24.503
I told him to. It was my idea.

19:24.504 --> 19:26.623
It's true,
I don't understand either,

19:26.624 --> 19:29.783
so don't ask. I don't want it.

19:29.784 --> 19:33.863
I want us to see other people.
I want an open relationship.

